At this point you can modify your netrhost.conf file settings in your game directory.
Using an editor modify the \(aqport\(aq and \(aqdebug_id\(aq respectively in your netrhost.conf as state.
The \(aqport\(aq will be the port the mush listens on, the debug_id is for the debug\-stack and is
your port with a \(aq5\(aq at the end.  So if your port is 4444, the debug_id is 44445
