(support for _/~ attribs)
.UNINDENT
.sp
You only need to do this if you received the RhostMUSH src.  If you received a binary, continue on to the next part.
.sp
To compile the code, just type \(aqmake confsource\(aq.  It will prompt you with settings on what you need to do.  If you just want to quickly hand edit the Makefile, it is in the directory src (full path src/Makefile).  Then you may just run \(aqmake source\(aq, if you so choose to hand\-edit the Makefile.
.sp
After the compile process is done, type:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
make links
.ft P
.fi
